Top of Page

Comments

Values from 13 to 25 must be shown on GUI if property Target Type under AccessCodes is set to TargetISCC only, meantime the values from 1 to 12 must be hidden.

For explanations of routing types, refer to the latest version of the T-Server Developer's Guide.
